{"pagelen": 100, "values": [{"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/61/comments/61050389.json"}, "code": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/diff/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake:b686ecc6d49f..c149694d8102?path=cmake%2FIgnPackaging.cmake"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/61/_/diff#comment-61050389"}}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 61, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/61.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/61"}}, "title": "Install cmake files to share instead of lib"}, "content": {"raw": "The use of `DATAROOT` and `SHARE` in these variables is inconsistent. Should we stick with one or the other? For example the set of variables could be `IGN_DATAROOT_INSTALL_DIR`, `IGN_DATAROOT_INSTALL_DIR_POSTFIX`, `IGN_DATAROOT_INSTALL_DIR`.\n\nI like `DATAROOT` more than `SHARE` because `SHARE` alludes to the `share` filesystem folder, which may not be actual place the installed files end up in the future.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>The use of <code>DATAROOT</code> and <code>SHARE</code> in these variables is inconsistent. Should we stick with one or the other? For example the set of variables could be <code>IGN_DATAROOT_INSTALL_DIR</code>, <code>IGN_DATAROOT_INSTALL_DIR_POSTFIX</code>, <code>IGN_DATAROOT_INSTALL_DIR</code>.</p>\n<p>I like <code>DATAROOT</code> more than <code>SHARE</code> because <code>SHARE</code> alludes to the <code>share</code> filesystem folder, which may not be actual place the installed files end up in the future.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2018-04-09T18:53:44.481899+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Nate Koenig", "uuid": "{c862cdd9-fcc8-4419-9fc7-e20db14b8fcb}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7Bc862cdd9-fcc8-4419-9fc7-e20db14b8fcb%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7Bc862cdd9-fcc8-4419-9fc7-e20db14b8fcb%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:095b1e12-74ed-4e20-b44f-2f0745b616e0/ca24bb11-4787-4b14-a20d-d91835e9bde2/128"}}, "nickname": "Nathan Koenig", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:095b1e12-74ed-4e20-b44f-2f0745b616e0"}, "inline": {"to": 109, "from": null, "path": "cmake/IgnPackaging.cmake"}, "updated_on": "2018-04-09T18:53:44.486071+00:00", "type": "pullrequest_comment", "id": 61050389}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/61/comments/61053381.json"}, "code": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/diff/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake:b686ecc6d49f..c149694d8102?path=cmake%2FIgnPackaging.cmake"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/61/_/diff#comment-61053381"}}, "parent": {"id": 61050389, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/61/comments/61050389.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/61/_/diff#comment-61050389"}}, "depth": 1}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 61, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/61.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/61"}}, "title": "Install cmake files to share instead of lib"}, "content": {"raw": "Would you suggest `IGN_DATAROOT_INSTALL_DIR_FULL` instead of `IGN_SHARE_INSTALL_DIR` so that it mirrors `IGN_INCLUDE_INSTALL_DIR_FULL`?", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Would you suggest <code>IGN_DATAROOT_INSTALL_DIR_FULL</code> instead of <code>IGN_SHARE_INSTALL_DIR</code> so that it mirrors <code>IGN_INCLUDE_INSTALL_DIR_FULL</code>?</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2018-04-09T19:30:30.208376+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Michael Grey", "uuid": "{c1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7Bc1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7Bc1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:67759e29-d1df-465f-868d-047738e36fc9/d42d74cf-c1bd-4431-8288-07f543bbe325/128"}}, "nickname": "mxgrey", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:67759e29-d1df-465f-868d-047738e36fc9"}, "inline": {"to": null, "from": null, "path": "cmake/IgnPackaging.cmake"}, "updated_on": "2018-04-09T19:30:30.212461+00:00", "type": "pullrequest_comment", "id": 61053381}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/61/comments/61053620.json"}, "code": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/diff/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake:b686ecc6d49f..c149694d8102?path=cmake%2FIgnPackaging.cmake"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/61/_/diff#comment-61053620"}}, "parent": {"id": 61053381, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/61/comments/61053381.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/61/_/diff#comment-61053381"}}, "depth": 2}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 61, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/61.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/61"}}, "title": "Install cmake files to share instead of lib"}, "content": {"raw": "One thing we need to be cautious of is that we'll need to have `share/ignition-cmake1/ignition-cmake1-config.cmake` rather than `share/ignition/ignition-cmake1/ignition-cmake1-config.cmake` so that cmake can find the project's config-file.\n\nThat makes me wonder if `IGN_DATAROOT_INSTALL_DIR_FULL` should be `share/ignition-cmake1/` instead of `share/ignition/ignition-cmake1`.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>One thing we need to be cautious of is that we'll need to have <code>share/ignition-cmake1/ignition-cmake1-config.cmake</code> rather than <code>share/ignition/ignition-cmake1/ignition-cmake1-config.cmake</code> so that cmake can find the project's config-file.</p>\n<p>That makes me wonder if <code>IGN_DATAROOT_INSTALL_DIR_FULL</code> should be <code>share/ignition-cmake1/</code> instead of <code>share/ignition/ignition-cmake1</code>.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2018-04-09T19:33:01.755307+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Michael Grey", "uuid": "{c1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7Bc1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7Bc1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:67759e29-d1df-465f-868d-047738e36fc9/d42d74cf-c1bd-4431-8288-07f543bbe325/128"}}, "nickname": "mxgrey", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:67759e29-d1df-465f-868d-047738e36fc9"}, "inline": {"to": null, "from": null, "path": "cmake/IgnPackaging.cmake"}, "updated_on": "2018-04-09T19:33:01.759515+00:00", "type": "pullrequest_comment", "id": 61053620}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/61/comments/61058535.json"}, "code": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/diff/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake:b686ecc6d49f..c149694d8102?path=cmake%2FIgnPackaging.cmake"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/61/_/diff#comment-61058535"}}, "parent": {"id": 61053620, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/61/comments/61053620.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/61/_/diff#comment-61053620"}}, "depth": 3}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 61, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/61.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/61"}}, "title": "Install cmake files to share instead of lib"}, "content": {"raw": "see [CMakeLists.txt:41](#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/61/install-cmake-files-to-share-instead-of/diff#LCMakeLists.txtT41); the config.cmake file is installed to `${IGN_DATAROOT_INSTALL_DIR}/cmake/${PROJECT_NAME_LOWER}`; it's not using these `IGN_SHARE_INSTALL_DIR*` variables", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>see <a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/61/install-cmake-files-to-share-instead-of/diff#LCMakeLists.txtT41\" rel=\"nofollow\">CMakeLists.txt:41</a>; the config.cmake file is installed to <code>${IGN_DATAROOT_INSTALL_DIR}/cmake/${PROJECT_NAME_LOWER}</code>; it's not using these <code>IGN_SHARE_INSTALL_DIR*</code> variables</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2018-04-09T20:29:39.621920+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Steve Peters", "uuid": "{2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1fb4816dad9e68337d3096f750951f6cd=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsSP-1.png"}}, "nickname": "Steven Peters", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:5de38267-b118-494c-aa76-4fab35448816"}, "inline": {"to": null, "from": null, "path": "cmake/IgnPackaging.cmake"}, "updated_on": "2018-04-09T20:29:39.625879+00:00", "type": "pullrequest_comment", "id": 61058535}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/61/comments/61059310.json"}, "code": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/diff/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake:b686ecc6d49f..c149694d8102?path=cmake%2FIgnPackaging.cmake"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/61/_/diff#comment-61059310"}}, "parent": {"id": 61058535, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/61/comments/61058535.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/61/_/diff#comment-61058535"}}, "depth": 4}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 61, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/61.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/61"}}, "title": "Install cmake files to share instead of lib"}, "content": {"raw": "That sounds fine to me, then.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>That sounds fine to me, then.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2018-04-09T20:38:03.918139+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Michael Grey", "uuid": "{c1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7Bc1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7Bc1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:67759e29-d1df-465f-868d-047738e36fc9/d42d74cf-c1bd-4431-8288-07f543bbe325/128"}}, "nickname": "mxgrey", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:67759e29-d1df-465f-868d-047738e36fc9"}, "inline": {"to": null, "from": null, "path": "cmake/IgnPackaging.cmake"}, "updated_on": "2018-04-09T20:38:03.920935+00:00", "type": "pullrequest_comment", "id": 61059310}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/61/comments/61190054.json"}, "code": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/diff/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake:b686ecc6d49f..c149694d8102?path=cmake%2FIgnPackaging.cmake"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/61/_/diff#comment-61190054"}}, "parent": {"id": 61050389, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/61/comments/61050389.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/61/_/diff#comment-61050389"}}, "depth": 1}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 61, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/61.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/61"}}, "title": "Install cmake files to share instead of lib"}, "content": {"raw": "Just bringing up the variable naming idea. Did you want to change the name, or keep it `SHARED`?", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Just bringing up the variable naming idea. Did you want to change the name, or keep it <code>SHARED</code>?</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2018-04-10T19:58:57.161178+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Nate Koenig", "uuid": "{c862cdd9-fcc8-4419-9fc7-e20db14b8fcb}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7Bc862cdd9-fcc8-4419-9fc7-e20db14b8fcb%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7Bc862cdd9-fcc8-4419-9fc7-e20db14b8fcb%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:095b1e12-74ed-4e20-b44f-2f0745b616e0/ca24bb11-4787-4b14-a20d-d91835e9bde2/128"}}, "nickname": "Nathan Koenig", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:095b1e12-74ed-4e20-b44f-2f0745b616e0"}, "inline": {"to": null, "from": null, "path": "cmake/IgnPackaging.cmake"}, "updated_on": "2018-04-10T19:58:57.164669+00:00", "type": "pullrequest_comment", "id": 61190054}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/61/comments/61190322.json"}, "code": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/diff/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake:b686ecc6d49f..c149694d8102?path=cmake%2FIgnPackaging.cmake"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/61/_/diff#comment-61190322"}}, "parent": {"id": 61190054, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/61/comments/61190054.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/61/_/diff#comment-61190054"}}, "depth": 2}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 61, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/61.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/61"}}, "title": "Install cmake files to share instead of lib"}, "content": {"raw": "I'd be supportive of either, since I think there are good arguments both ways. `DATAROOT` is more general, which is good for taking alternative filesystems into account, but `SHARE` is likely to invoke more familiarity for most of our developers, since we're all generally accustomed to UNIX-like systems.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>I'd be supportive of either, since I think there are good arguments both ways. <code>DATAROOT</code> is more general, which is good for taking alternative filesystems into account, but <code>SHARE</code> is likely to invoke more familiarity for most of our developers, since we're all generally accustomed to UNIX-like systems.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2018-04-10T20:02:02.195014+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Michael Grey", "uuid": "{c1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7Bc1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7Bc1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:67759e29-d1df-465f-868d-047738e36fc9/d42d74cf-c1bd-4431-8288-07f543bbe325/128"}}, "nickname": "mxgrey", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:67759e29-d1df-465f-868d-047738e36fc9"}, "inline": {"to": null, "from": null, "path": "cmake/IgnPackaging.cmake"}, "updated_on": "2018-04-10T20:02:02.198747+00:00", "type": "pullrequest_comment", "id": 61190322}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/61/comments/61190417.json"}, "code": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/diff/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake:b686ecc6d49f..c149694d8102?path=cmake%2FIgnPackaging.cmake"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/61/_/diff#comment-61190417"}}, "parent": {"id": 61190322, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/61/comments/61190322.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/61/_/diff#comment-61190322"}}, "depth": 3}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 61, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/61.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/61"}}, "title": "Install cmake files to share instead of lib"}, "content": {"raw": "In support of `DATADIR` or `DATAROOTDIR`, those are the terms used by [`GNUInstallDirs`](https://cmake.org/cmake/help/v3.5/module/GNUInstallDirs.html).", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>In support of <code>DATADIR</code> or <code>DATAROOTDIR</code>, those are the terms used by <a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"https://cmake.org/cmake/help/v3.5/module/GNUInstallDirs.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><code>GNUInstallDirs</code></a>.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2018-04-10T20:03:29.435009+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Michael Grey", "uuid": "{c1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7Bc1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7Bc1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:67759e29-d1df-465f-868d-047738e36fc9/d42d74cf-c1bd-4431-8288-07f543bbe325/128"}}, "nickname": "mxgrey", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:67759e29-d1df-465f-868d-047738e36fc9"}, "inline": {"to": null, "from": null, "path": "cmake/IgnPackaging.cmake"}, "updated_on": "2018-04-10T20:03:29.438563+00:00", "type": "pullrequest_comment", "id": 61190417}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/61/comments/61223455.json"}, "code": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/diff/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake:b686ecc6d49f..c149694d8102?path=cmake%2FIgnPackaging.cmake"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/61/_/diff#comment-61223455"}}, "parent": {"id": 61050389, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/61/comments/61050389.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/61/_/diff#comment-61050389"}}, "depth": 1}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 61, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/61.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/61"}}, "title": "Install cmake files to share instead of lib"}, "content": {"raw": "There's two locations that I want variables for. For example, when installing `ignition-math5` to `/usr`:\n\n* `/usr/share` (currently named `IGN_DATAROOT_INSTALL_DIR` or `CMAKE_INSTALL_DATAROOTDIR`)\n* `/usr/share/ignition/ignition-math5` (currently named `IGN_SHARE_INSTALL_DIR`)\n\nThe `IGN_SHARE_INSTALL_DIR_POSTFIX` is helpful for constructing `IGN_SHARE_INSTALL_DIR`.\n\nI suppose we could just use `CMAKE_INSTALL_DATAROOTDIR` to refer to  `/usr/share` in that example and change the two `IGN_SHARE_INSTALL_DIR*` variables to `IGN_DATA_INSTALL_DIR*` (not DATAROOT, since it's not pointing at the root). I'll go ahead and make this change, and await further comment", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>There's two locations that I want variables for. For example, when installing <code>ignition-math5</code> to <code>/usr</code>:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>/usr/share</code> (currently named <code>IGN_DATAROOT_INSTALL_DIR</code> or <code>CMAKE_INSTALL_DATAROOTDIR</code>)</li>\n<li><code>/usr/share/ignition/ignition-math5</code> (currently named <code>IGN_SHARE_INSTALL_DIR</code>)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>The <code>IGN_SHARE_INSTALL_DIR_POSTFIX</code> is helpful for constructing <code>IGN_SHARE_INSTALL_DIR</code>.</p>\n<p>I suppose we could just use <code>CMAKE_INSTALL_DATAROOTDIR</code> to refer to  <code>/usr/share</code> in that example and change the two <code>IGN_SHARE_INSTALL_DIR*</code> variables to <code>IGN_DATA_INSTALL_DIR*</code> (not DATAROOT, since it's not pointing at the root). I'll go ahead and make this change, and await further comment</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2018-04-11T07:04:28.825192+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Steve Peters", "uuid": "{2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1fb4816dad9e68337d3096f750951f6cd=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsSP-1.png"}}, "nickname": "Steven Peters", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:5de38267-b118-494c-aa76-4fab35448816"}, "inline": {"to": null, "from": null, "path": "cmake/IgnPackaging.cmake"}, "updated_on": "2018-04-11T19:15:27.250923+00:00", "type": "pullrequest_comment", "id": 61223455}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/61/comments/61223989.json"}, "code": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/diff/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake:b686ecc6d49f..c149694d8102?path=cmake%2FIgnPackaging.cmake"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/61/_/diff#comment-61223989"}}, "parent": {"id": 61223455, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ign