"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/61/_/diff#comment-61223989"}}, "depth": 3}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 61, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/61.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/61"}}, "title": "Install cmake files to share instead of lib"}, "content": {"raw": "I've merged this forward to pull request #63 and will continue to merge forward if people are happy with the change", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>I've merged this forward to <a href=\"#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/63/fake-install-part-1-use-complete-file\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"ap-connect-link\">pull request #63</a> and will continue to merge forward if people are happy with the change</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2018-04-11T19:15:12.837242+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Steve Peters", "uuid": "{2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1fb4816dad9e68337d3096f750951f6cd=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsSP-1.png"}}, "nickname": "Steven Peters", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:5de38267-b118-494c-aa76-4fab35448816"}, "inline": {"to": null, "from": null, "path": "cmake/IgnPackaging.cmake"}, "updated_on": "2018-04-11T19:15:12.840660+00:00", "type": "pullrequest_comment", "id": 61316828}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/61/comments/61318338.json"}, "code": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/diff/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake:dafcb0665d19..4c299795ada1?path=cmake%2FIgnPackaging.cmake"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/61/_/diff#comment-61318338"}}, "parent": {"id": 61316828, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/61/comments/61316828.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/61/_/diff#comment-61316828"}}, "depth": 4}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 61, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/61.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/61"}}, "title": "Install cmake files to share instead of lib"}, "content": {"raw": "Using `DATA` instead of `DATAROOT` is reasonable.\n\n+1", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Using <code>DATA</code> instead of <code>DATAROOT</code> is reasonable.</p>\n<p>+1</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2018-04-11T19:33:11.711781+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Michael Grey", "uuid": "{c1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7Bc1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7Bc1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:67759e29-d1df-465f-868d-047738e36fc9/d42d74cf-c1bd-4431-8288-07f543bbe325/128"}}, "nickname": "mxgrey", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:67759e29-d1df-465f-868d-047738e36fc9"}, "inline": {"to": null, "from": null, "path": "cmake/IgnPackaging.cmake"}, "updated_on": "2018-04-11T19:33:11.720072+00:00", "type": "pullrequest_comment", "id": 61318338}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/61/comments/61183590.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/61/_/diff#comment-61183590"}}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 61, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/61.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/61"}}, "title": "Install cmake files to share instead of lib"}, "content": {"raw": "Just to be sure: when we mean architecture-independent we mean that there is no mention to an arch \\(specially arch dependent paths\\) inside the cmake files, right?", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Just to be sure: when we mean architecture-independent we mean that there is no mention to an arch (specially arch dependent paths) inside the cmake files, right?</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2018-04-10T18:40:51.881919+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Jose Luis Rivero", "uuid": "{d12309b2-f745-42ee-b119-aec4fcdf81fe}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7Bd12309b2-f745-42ee-b119-aec4fcdf81fe%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7Bd12309b2-f745-42ee-b119-aec4fcdf81fe%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/109284c8b83411dbc7492138f6167e9ed=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsJR-5.png"}}, "nickname": "Jose Luis Rivero", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:155a32e2-420c-4d50-98e0-0e722f63f906"}, "updated_on": "2018-04-10T18:40:51.886433+00:00", "type": "pullrequest_comment", "id": 61183590}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/61/comments/61184085.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/61/_/diff#comment-61184085"}}, "parent": {"id": 61183590, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/61/comments/61183590.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/61/_/diff#comment-61183590"}}, "depth": 1}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 61, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/61.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/61"}}, "title": "Install cmake files to share instead of lib"}, "content": {"raw": "That is correct. These cmake modules and supplementary build resources are all independent of architecture, so it should be completely safe to install one copy of all of them in a directory that is architecture-agnostic (i.e. `share`).", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>That is correct. These cmake modules and supplementary build resources are all independent of architecture, so it should be completely safe to install one copy of all of them in a directory that is architecture-agnostic (i.e. <code>share</code>).</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2018-04-10T18:46:19.005665+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Michael Grey", "uuid": "{c1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7Bc1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7Bc1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:67759e29-d1df-465f-868d-047738e36fc9/d42d74cf-c1bd-4431-8288-07f543bbe325/128"}}, "nickname": "mxgrey", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:67759e29-d1df-465f-868d-047738e36fc9"}, "updated_on": "2018-04-10T18:46:19.011637+00:00", "type": "pullrequest_comment", "id": 61184085}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/61/comments/61318469.json"}, "code": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/diff/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake:dafcb0665d19..4c299795ada1?path=config%2Fignition-cmake-config.cmake.in"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/61/_/diff#comment-61318469"}}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 61, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/61.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/61"}}, "title": "Install cmake files to share instead of lib"}, "content": {"raw": "I don't see where `PACKAGE_IGN_DATA_INSTALL_DIR` ever gets set. Was this meant to be `IGN_DATA_INSTALL_DIR`?", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>I don't see where <code>PACKAGE_IGN_DATA_INSTALL_DIR</code> ever gets set. Was this meant to be <code>IGN_DATA_INSTALL_DIR</code>?</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2018-04-11T19:34:57.818421+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Michael Grey", "uuid": "{c1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7Bc1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7Bc1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:67759e29-d1df-465f-868d-047738e36fc9/d42d74cf-c1bd-4431-8288-07f543bbe325/128"}}, "nickname": "mxgrey", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:67759e29-d1df-465f-868d-047738e36fc9"}, "inline": {"to": 56, "from": null, "path": "config/ignition-cmake-config.cmake.in"}, "updated_on": "2018-04-11T19:34:57.833820+00:00", "type": "pullrequest_comment", "id": 61318469}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/61/comments/61322602.json"}, "code": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/diff/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake:dafcb0665d19..4c299795ada1?path=config%2Fignition-cmake-config.cmake.in"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/61/_/diff#comment-61322602"}}, "parent": {"id": 61318469, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/61/comments/61318469.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/61/_/diff#comment-61318469"}}, "depth": 1}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 61, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/61.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/61"}}, "title": "Install cmake files to share instead of lib"}, "content": {"raw": "It's set by code related to the `@PACKAGE_INIT@` call above and the `PATH_VARS` field in the root CMakeLists.txt. Here's some documentation; look for the list of 4 steps:\n\n* https://cmake.org/cmake/help/v3.5/module/CMakePackageConfigHelpers.html\n\nI'll answer any follow-up questions you have after taking a look at that", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>It's set by code related to the <code>@PACKAGE_INIT@</code> call above and the <code>PATH_VARS</code> field in the root CMakeLists.txt. Here's some documentation; look for the list of 4 steps:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://cmake.org/cmake/help/v3.5/module/CMakePackageConfigHelpers.html\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"ap-connect-link\">https://cmake.org/cmake/help/v3.5/module/CMakePackageConfigHelpers.html</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>I'll answer any follow-up questions you have after taking a look at that</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2018-04-11T20:26:32.397622+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Steve Peters", "uuid": "{2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1fb4816dad9e68337d3096f750951f6cd=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsSP-1.png"}}, "nickname": "Steven Peters", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:5de38267-b118-494c-aa76-4fab35448816"}, "inline": {"to": null, "from": null, "path": "config/ignition-cmake-config.cmake.in"}, "updated_on": "2018-04-11T20:26:32.408283+00:00", "type": "pullrequest_comment", "id": 61322602}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/61/comments/61323476.json"}, "code": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/diff/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake:dafcb0665d19..4c299795ada1?path=config%2Fignition-cmake-config.cmake.in"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/61/_/diff#comment-61323476"}}, "parent": {"id": 61322602, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/61/comments/61322602.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/61/_/diff#comment-61322602"}}, "depth": 2}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 61, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/61.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/61"}}, "title": "Install cmake files to share instead of lib"}, "content": {"raw": "That makes sense, thanks!", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>That makes sense, thanks!</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2018-04-11T20:38:20.217062+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Michael Grey", "uuid": "{c1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7Bc1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7Bc1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:67759e29-d1df-465f-868d-047738e36fc9/d42d74cf-c1bd-4431-8288-07f543bbe325/128"}}, "nickname": "mxgrey", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:67759e29-d1df-465f-868d-047738e36fc9"}, "inline": {"to": null, "from": null, "path": "config/ignition-cmake-config.cmake.in"}, "updated_on": "2018-04-11T20:38:20.223793+00:00", "type": "pullrequest_comment", "id": 61323476}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/61/comments/61329769.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/61/_/diff#comment-61329769"}}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 61, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/61.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/61"}}, "title": "Install cmake files to share instead of lib"}, "content": {"raw": "I was able to use it together with ign-math without problems. The CI is happy. I've notice that when installing the files using DESTDIR \\(i.e. `DESTDIR=/tmp/foo make install`\\) there are some `$HOME` paths that end up being installed there, but the problem is also present in `default` ", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>I was able to use it together with ign-math without problems. The CI is happy. I've notice that when installing the files using DESTDIR (i.e. <code>DESTDIR=/tmp/foo make install</code>) there are some <code>$HOME</code> paths that end up being installed there, but the problem is also present in <code>default</code> </p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2018-04-11T22:07:43.574521+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Jose Luis Rivero", "uuid": "{d12309b2-f745-42ee-b119-aec4fcdf81fe}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7Bd12309b2-f745-42ee-b119-aec4fcdf81fe%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7Bd12309b2-f745-42ee-b119-aec4fcdf81fe%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/109284c8b83411dbc7492138f6167e9ed=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsJR-5.png"}}, "nickname": "Jose Luis Rivero", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:155a32e2-420c-4d50-98e0-0e722f63f906"}, "updated_on": "2018-04-11T22:07:43.581826+00:00", "type": "pullrequest_comment", "id": 61329769}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/61/comments/61332209.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/61/_/diff#comment-61332209"}}, "parent": {"id": 61329769, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/61/comments/61329769.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/61/_/diff#comment-61329769"}}, "depth": 1}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 61, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/61.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/61"}}, "title": "Install cmake files to share instead of lib"}, "content": {"raw": "To elaborate on Jose's comment, it seems that trying to use `make DESTDIR=/dest/dir install` has some rather problematic behavior. Apparently `DESTDIR=/dest/dir` will prefix the install paths (including `CMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX`) with `/dest/dir`. So if `CMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX` was `/usr/local`, then `make DESTDIR=/dest/dir install` will have the installed files go to `/dest/dir/usr/local`.\n\nThis is problematic because the example projects (which are set to be installed to `/path/to/build/folder/install`) will inadvertently get installed to `/dest/dir/path/to/build/folder/install`, which is **outside** of the build directory.\n\nWe need a way of removing the build and installation of the example projects from the build and installation of `all` (preferably by tying those to `make test` instead), or else we won't be able to correctly support `make DESTDIR=<path> install`.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>To elaborate on Jose's comment, it seems that trying to use <code>make DESTDIR=/dest/dir install</code> has some rather problematic behavior. Apparently <code>DESTDIR=/dest/dir</code> will prefix the install paths (including <code>CMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX</code>) with <code>/dest/dir</code>. So if <code>CMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX</code> was <code>/usr/local</code>, then <code>make DESTDIR=/dest/dir install</code> will have the installed files go to <code>/dest/dir/usr/local</code>.</p>\n<p>This is problematic because the example projects (which are set to be installed to <code>/path/to/build/folder/install</code>) will inadvertently get installed to <code>/dest/dir/path/to/build/folder/install</code>, which is <strong>outside</strong> of the build directory.</p>\n<p>We need a way of removing the build and installation of the example projects from the build and installation of <code>all</code> (preferably by tying those to <code>make test</code> instead), or else we won't be able to correctly support <code>make DESTDIR=&lt;path&gt; install</code>.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2018-04-11T22:50:05.315626+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Michael Grey", "uuid": "{c1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7Bc1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7Bc1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:67759e29-d1df-465f-868d-047738e36fc9/d42d74cf-c1bd-4431-8288-07f543bbe325/128"}}, "nickname": "mxgrey", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:67759e29-d1df-465f-868d-047738e36fc9"}, "updated_on": "2018-04-11T22:50:48.610381+00:00", "type": "pullrequest_comment", "id": 61332209}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/61/comments/61334105.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/61/_/diff#comment-61334105"}}, "parent": {"id": 61332209, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/61/comments/61332209.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/61/_/diff#comment-61332209"}}, "depth": 2}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 61, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pullrequests/61.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-cmake/pull-requests/61"}}, "title": "Install cmake files to share instead of lib"}, "content": {"raw": "Maybe we can move this to an issue since it is already present on default?", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Maybe we can move this to an issue since it is already present on default?</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2018-04-11T23: